n splitting servers until people yell on Gameplay. The GM apparently took that as a personal insult against him/her/it, and basically started bitching at me and telling me to quit or shut up. Interestingly, it "left" the chat channel very, very shortly afterwards, and was replaced.</FONT></TD></TR></TABLE>
